ActStandards Council of Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of MICHAEL KEVIN BURNS of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, to be a member of the Standards Council of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Merete Heggelund, whose term has expired.
